value.0: Greetings to you stranger, I am afraid you have fallen upon us at an ill time. Two weeks ago we discovered the crypt of our founder member was violated and his remains desecrated. Since that foul night, many of our brothers have gone missing. Stolen off into the night, to brighter pastures no doubt. I don't know if this temple can remain open.

Yes it is dreadful indeed, but please, do not allow our situation to prevent you from spending a while with us. Take this Token and enjoy our facilities. Your journey will be far better traveled if you are rested.

I see you are a follower of the older ways <brother/sister>. Is there anyway that I could persuade you to rise above our current situation and join our ranks?
Although I must admit that in these sad times our spiritual guidance can be somewhat lacking, we do however, outfit members of our order well.
Perhaps you might stay around for a few days while I confer with council members about that. Usually such a gift would require a great service to the order.

Less Haste, More Speed. You show Wisdom <brother/sister>. Take this Token and enjoy our hospitality, while I confer with the council. As I have already said, our orders members have dwindled lately, so there could well be something you could do for us.
Our order is a simple order. We have simple needs.

Haste does not always get you there quicker <brother/sister>. Take this Token and enjoy our hospitality, while I confer with the council. As I have already said, our orders members have dwindled lately, so there could well be something you could do for us.
Perhaps you might stay around for a few days so I can talk to the council members about that. Often a chore of some kind is required for initiation of new members.
Take this Token and enjoy our hospitality, while I confer with the council.
Ahh, hello again. How are you enjoying your stay with us?
Peace and Tranquility are good for the soul my friend.
Oh My, I see you have the remains of our founder member.  May I ask how you came to have this in your possession?
I had feared as much but could not prove anything. Accusations without proof, become a double edged blade, often wounding the wielder instead.
You have my thanks.  We shall investigate these caves and root out any members who are not acting according to the principals of this order!
Please take these Initiate's Robes as a token of our esteemed thanks and go with the graces of the White Crane School.
Please take these Master Robes as a token of our esteemed thanks and go with the graces of the White Crane School.
Ahhh, <FirstName>. It is a pleasure to see you again, I hope all is well with you.
Thats Dreadful.
I am not interested in your order or your outfitting, thank you.
I am not interested in joining an order at this moment. I am on my road for self enlightenment. I could however, benefit from the gift of a robe.
No, it's OK. Don't trouble yourself, I'll just move along.
I would be willing to wait for such an answer.
I would be willing to preform such a service.
Oh, OK then. Perhaps another time.
No. It's OK thank you. I'll just move along.
OK. Thank you.
Joining your order would be an honor. How would I go about that?
Don't go through all that trouble for me. Thanks anyway.
I will stay, thank you for your consideration.
Thank you.
The environment here is much more peaceful than I am used to.
Well I'd like to say the Peace and Tranquility has been good for my soul, BUT.......<StartAction>Remove Skull from Pack.</Start>

I took it from the hands of a very nasty Demon hiding away in some hidden caves below the monastery. 
There is a secret passage in your basement leading to an old shaft that descends to them.
I'm afraid it looks as though your order has been infiltrated by monks with some evil purpose.
I have dealt them a powerful blow and I am quite sure their leader is now dead.
You are welcome. I am glad to be of service. Perhaps now your order can start on its road to recovery and flourish once again.
Thank you very much.
Thank you very much.
